1
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:04,760
Thank you, Ms. Xue.

2
00:01:06,319 --> 00:01:07,439
Just a heads-up,

3
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:08,480
young lady,

4
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:10,680
this jade is from the shady side,

5
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:12,920
which is considered unlucky.

6
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:14,840
Too bad,

7
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:16,280
I specialize in dispelling bad luck.

8
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:24,879
Give me the laptop.

9
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,879
What do you mean

10
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,159
by digital currency?

11
00:01:45,159 --> 00:01:46,000
Where's my stuff?

12
00:01:46,239 --> 00:01:47,319
I should be asking you the same.

13
00:01:47,879 --> 00:01:49,640
Send a woman to rob me?

14
00:01:50,359 --> 00:01:51,959
Get her back.

15
00:01:51,959 --> 00:01:53,159
Bring me the box.

16
00:01:53,159 --> 00:01:54,640
Get the box back.

17
00:01:57,159 --> 00:01:58,719
You come with me. Watch it.

18
00:02:00,519 --> 00:02:00,959
Master,

19
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,920
Xue Li's bodyguards are heading your way.

20
00:02:03,239 --> 00:02:04,040
Roger that.

21
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,520
Could you check if this jade pendant

22
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,520
if my jade pendant

23
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:31,120
matches the broken piece

24
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,120
I just took a picture of.

25
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,680
Is Jiang Xun

26
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,400
just here for the repair?

27
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,479
70,000.

28
00:02:42,159 --> 00:02:43,199
80,000.

29
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,400
100,000.

30
00:02:44,599 --> 00:02:45,719
150,000.

31
00:02:46,159 --> 00:02:47,719
Why did she suddenly stop bidding?

32
00:02:47,719 --> 00:02:48,680
[Is 150,000 yuan]

33
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,319
[the agreed-upon price with Xue Li?]

34
00:02:50,319 --> 00:02:51,560
[Jiang Xun took the lead.]

35
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:52,520
Hello, mom.

36
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,319
Did you receive the red scarf

37
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,560
I bought for you?

38
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,080
Red scarf?

39
00:02:58,159 --> 00:02:59,080
What red scarf?

40
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:02,080
Is it this red-haired guy?

41
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:03,639
I received it.

42
00:03:05,919 --> 00:03:06,840
Good, that's good.

43
00:03:14,719 --> 00:03:15,520
Excuse me.

44
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:17,879
Excuse me.

45
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,639
Excuse me.

46
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:33,840
Excuse me.

47
00:03:37,719 --> 00:03:39,159
Mr. Shen has a strange taste.

48
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,159
He's a man.

49
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,759
Can't you see his Adam's apple?

50
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:45,960
One hundred thousand.

51
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,080
Excuse me.

52
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,159
Excuse me.

53
00:04:18,439 --> 00:04:20,720
Wei Chuan, keep looking for the red hair.

54
00:04:21,199 --> 00:04:22,319
I'll go back and keep an eye on Jiang Xun.

55
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,480
Roger that.

56
00:04:25,199 --> 00:04:26,319
Let me see where you are.

57
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,439
I found her.

58
00:04:36,759 --> 00:04:37,560
Sorry,

59
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:40,120
please come with us.

60
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,120
What?

61
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,160
You've already paid.

62
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,759
Do you want to take the goods back?

63
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,199
You're here.

64
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,600
Why are you here?

65
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:53,480
Mr. Shen, don't meddle in this.

66
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,319
[I'm her husband.]

67
00:04:58,879 --> 00:05:00,199
[Only by cooperating with him]

68
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,959
[can we get through this temporarily.]

69
00:05:02,199 --> 00:05:04,160
What's going on with you two?

70
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,319
What do you mean?

71
00:05:05,519 --> 00:05:06,759
He is my husband.

72
00:05:06,959 --> 00:05:08,639
Have you heard of Shen Group?

73
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,680
You can't afford to mess with them.

74
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:11,680
I'm the young mistress of Shen Group.

75
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,759
You'd better not mess with me.

76
00:05:14,959 --> 00:05:15,920
Darling,

77
00:05:16,519 --> 00:05:17,360
I'm sorry.

78
00:05:17,639 --> 00:05:19,680
I shouldn't have broken the thing you gave me.

79
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:20,800
It's okay.

80
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,319
We can buy another one.

81
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:23,920
Mom is waiting for us at the B2.

82
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:24,759
Let's go back first.

83
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,319
It's all a misunderstanding.

84
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,839
A misunderstanding, let's go.

85
00:05:31,319 --> 00:05:32,639
I said it's a misunderstanding.

86
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,360
Master, I'm calling for backup.

87
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:10,839
Hello.

88
00:06:10,839 --> 00:06:11,879
Master.

89
00:06:11,879 --> 00:06:12,879
Can you hear me?

90
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:13,839
Hello.

91
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,519
Oh, my. They are fighting.

92
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:23,959
Master.

93
00:06:23,959 --> 00:06:25,560
They are too many. Go now.

94
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:44,720
Run.

95
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,560
Stop.

96
00:06:45,879 --> 00:06:46,720
Don't run.

97
00:06:46,959 --> 00:06:47,800
Stop!

98
00:06:57,439 --> 00:06:58,120
Stop!

99
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:02,639
Master, where are you?

100
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,319
Boss, we got the jade back.

101
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:36,639
That man said he's the heir of Shen Group.

102
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,519
That woman said she's his wife.

103
00:07:39,839 --> 00:07:41,720
The heir of Shen Group is not easy to deal with.

104
00:07:41,759 --> 00:07:42,800
As for that woman,

105
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,120
you decide.

106
00:07:44,319 --> 00:07:45,639
But be clean.

107
00:07:46,399 --> 00:07:47,199
Got it.

108
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:54,600
Hello.

109
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:57,160
The incident today caused too much noise.

110
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,560
Xu Mo doesn't want to trade with us now.

111
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:01,160
His mother needs imported medicine for her cancer.

112
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:02,279
You talk to him nicely.

113
00:08:02,279 --> 00:08:03,040
Ask him to bring the goods

114
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,439
to the Rongzhou Museum of Folk Customs for trade.

115
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,319
I'll double the money.

116
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,360
Do we really have to break the law?

117
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,360
Don't worry.

118
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:10,519
I have a foolproof plan.

119
00:08:10,519 --> 00:08:11,399
It's absolutely safe.

120
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:16,600
Looks like I need to buy insurance for myself.

121
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,439
Go to the airport.

122
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,440
Mr. Shen,

123
00:08:41,399 --> 00:08:43,240
what are you trying to do with this?

124
00:08:47,519 --> 00:08:49,480
Cracking down on underground auctions

125
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,279
is everyone's responsibility.

126
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,960
Some of you

127
00:08:54,519 --> 00:08:55,919
are too greedy.

128
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:59,039
and have infringed on my business.

129
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,879
That's it?

130
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:13,480
Do you think we are afraid to kill

131
00:09:13,639 --> 00:09:14,840
because we are gangsters?

132
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:17,200
If I don't go back this afternoon,

133
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,720
my men

134
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:22,919
will take down your club.

135
00:09:29,759 --> 00:09:32,039
Guys, Mr. Shen is in trouble.

136
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,440
Let's go and save him.

137
00:09:33,639 --> 00:09:34,480
Yes.

138
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:35,159
Let's go.

139
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,320
Name your price.

140
00:10:20,279 --> 00:10:21,080
How much do you want?

141
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,000
Let me go.

142
00:10:23,399 --> 00:10:24,919
You and your wife were living well.

143
00:10:24,919 --> 00:10:26,480
Why did you get into this trouble?

144
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,960
The point is, it's not me who wants your life now.

145
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,000
It's our boss.

146
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,039
Who is your boss?

147
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:32,279
You'd better not know that.

148
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,559
But that woman

149
00:10:34,559 --> 00:10:35,759
is probably not going to stay.

150
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,559
She offended my boss.

151
00:10:37,679 --> 00:10:38,519
I won't let her off the hook.

152
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,559
If you dare to hurt her,

153
00:10:42,559 --> 00:10:43,679
I won't let you go.

154
00:10:47,559 --> 00:10:48,039
Wait.

155
00:10:48,039 --> 00:10:49,559
Are you two really a couple?

156
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,159
She didn't tell me that.

157
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:53,799
What's your relationship?

158
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,519
Is he your husband?

159
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,120
He's not my husband.

160
00:11:27,159 --> 00:11:29,600
According to Article 150 of the Criminal Law

161
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:32,159
of the People's Republic of China,

162
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:34,759
the national security agency

163
00:11:34,759 --> 00:11:35,559
can adopt technical investigation measures

164
00:11:35,559 --> 00:11:37,440
for national security crimes

165
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:39,639
after filing a case

166
00:11:39,639 --> 00:11:41,679
and with strict approval procedures

167
00:11:41,679 --> 00:11:44,440
according to the need of investigation.

168
00:11:44,879 --> 00:11:47,120
In the drama, Jiang Xun

169
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:49,080
accidentally entered a spy trade scene.

170
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,960
Shen Shutu and Wei Chuan

171
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:53,840
investigated a major espionage case.

172
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:55,360
According to the law,

173
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:58,480
they can obtain the content of the conversation

174
00:11:58,679 --> 00:12:01,120
and extract and fix criminal evidence legally.
